### Agents — stateless run + persisted run-by-order
###
### Both endpoints invoke the Analyst Agent (live Claude call ≈ $0.02 each).
### The stateless variant takes a full OrderDTO in the body and returns the
### result without persisting. The by-order variant takes just an order_id,
### loads the order + recent history from DB, and persists an AgentSuggestion.

@host = http://localhost:8000

# @name login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin123


# ============================================================================
# POST /api/agents/analyst/run — stateless, body-driven
# ============================================================================
### Looks normal — agent should approve
POST {{host}}/api/agents/analyst/run
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order": {
    "orderNumber": "PO-DEMO-001",
    "orderDate": "2026-04-25T10:00:00Z",
    "expectedDeliveryDate": "2026-05-02T10:00:00Z",
    "retailerCode": "CARREFOUR-ES",
    "retailerName": "Carrefour España SA",
    "supplierCode": "IBERIAN-FOODS",
    "supplierName": "Iberian Foods SL",
    "currencyCode": "EUR",
    "totalAmount": 124250,
    "lineItems": [
      {
        "lineNumber": 1,
        "productCode": "SKU-OIL-EVO-1L",
        "productName": "Extra Virgin Olive Oil 1L",
        "quantity": 100,
        "unitPrice": 595,
        "lineTotal": 59500
      },
      {
        "lineNumber": 2,
        "productCode": "SKU-HAM-IBERICO-200G",
        "productName": "Iberian Ham 200g",
        "quantity": 50,
        "unitPrice": 1295,
        "lineTotal": 64750
      }
    ]
  },
  "recentOrders": []
}

###

### Anomalous order — agent should escalate
POST {{host}}/api/agents/analyst/run
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order": {
    "orderNumber": "PO-WEIRD-002",
    "orderDate": "2026-04-25T10:00:00Z",
    "retailerCode": "LEROY-ES",
    "retailerName": "Leroy Merlin España",
    "supplierCode": "IBERIAN-FOODS",
    "supplierName": "Iberian Foods SL",
    "currencyCode": "EUR",
    "totalAmount": 13500000,
    "lineItems": [
      {
        "lineNumber": 1,
        "productCode": "SKU-LUXURY-WATCH",
        "productName": "Diamond Watch",
        "quantity": 999,
        "unitPrice": 13513,
        "lineTotal": 13499487
      }
    ]
  },
  "recentOrders": []
}


# ============================================================================
# POST /api/agents/analyst/run/by-order/{order_id} — persisted
# ============================================================================
### Pick an order_id from `GET /api/orders?status=pending_review` first.
POST {{host}}/api/agents/analyst/run/by-order/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000?recent_limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### Unknown order → 404
POST {{host}}/api/agents/analyst/run/by-order/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
